ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This year, a general course on semiparametric and non-parametric estimation and inference, focused primarily on the method of sieves. I would recommend the course particularly to students with an interest in applying these these methods, though probably not to someone with only a casual interest in the topic.
If they were interested in semi/nonparametric econometrics, then of course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course introduced me to some general ideas that I might use in future research.
The course provided several ideas for future research.
